Divine Pilgrimage

Pilgrimage is a patron activity. After pledging to Mitra, Gaea, or Set, you
may begin a pilgrimage and visit divine shrines before the omen-thread grows
cold.

Commands:

  patron pilgrimage start
  patron pilgrimage status
  look token

You must have a patron before beginning a pilgrimage. Completing one can earn
patron favor and help tie your character more closely to the divine cycle.

Related help:

  help divine
  help patron
  help shrine
